On an unknown date, [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] wrote '''[[Letters not published in "The Letters of J.R.R. Tolkien"|a letter]] to [[Simonne d'Ardenne]]'''.<ref name=JRRVF>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.jrrvf.com/forum/noncgi/Forum3/HTML/000234.html|articlename=Tolkien & Simonne d'Ardenne (Oxford-Liège-Oxford) |dated=|website=[http://www.jrrvf.com/haut.shtml JRRVF.com]|accessed=20 May 2012}}</ref>

*'''Subject:''' ''[[Wikipedia:Fagrskinna|Fagrskinna]]'', philological discussion of ''[[Wiktionary:berserk|berserk]]''.
*'''Publication:''' None.
*'''Archive:''' The letter is kept at the [[Wikipedia:University of Liège|University of Liège]], with the following description in French: "[J.R.R. Tolkien], extrait d’une lettre [adressée à S.R.T.O. d’Ardenne], non datée, sur papier jaune pâle."<ref name=JRRVF/>
